OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FWords by Benedict Elliot
OL,9,FTradespeople have hit out at thieves
OL,10,Fwho target vans storing tools and kit.
OL,11,FIt comes as one Welsh police force
OL,12,Freports a 31% rise in incidents.
OL,14,FGwent Police recorded an increase from
OL,15,F29 to 38 incidents while a Freedom of
OL,16,FInformation (FoI) request found that
OL,17,Fat least #40 million worth of tools
OL,18,Fwere stolen across the UK from 2023-
OL,19,F2024. It means almost four in five
OL,20,Ftradespeople have suffered a tool
OL,21,Ftheft.
