OL,7,FPlumber Robbie Hawkins was left
OL,8,Ffeeling "violated" after more than
OL,9,F#3,000 worth of tools was stolen from
OL,10,Fhis van.
OL,12,FJust after midnight on May 8, his
OL,13,FTransit Custom van that was parked
OL,14,Fnear his home was broken into by
OL,15,Fthieves who used a master key to
OL,16,Funlock the side door.
OL,18,FEquipment including his #2,000 press
OL,19,Fgun and all his power tools, drills
OL,20,Fand angle grinders were taken within a
OL,21,Fminute.
