OL,7,F"Everything I had worked for all my
OL,8,Flife was taken away from me," said Mr
OL,9,FHawkins.
OL,11,FThe 38-year-old continued: "This is
OL,12,Fhappening to tradespeople in Wales
OL,13,Fevery day.
OL,15,F"I broke down when I realised what
OL,16,Fhappened. I've been left with
OL,17,Fnightmares and PTSD, and I now have
OL,18,Fthis constant feeling of anxiety when
OL,19,FI go to work."
