OL,7,FMr Hawkins, who works across mid and
OL,8,Fsouth Wales, has since considered
OL,9,Fleaving the trades industry.
OL,11,FHe said: "I've been a plumber since I
OL,12,Fwas 16 and I love my job, but it's not
OL,13,Fpractical to carry on when you lose
OL,14,Fincome and have to buy new tools. This
OL,15,Fshouldn't be happening to hard working
OL,16,Fpeople.
OL,18,F"These are tools you need to stay in
OL,19,Fwork so you can feed your family."
