OL,7,FCCTV footage showing a man taking
OL,8,Ftools from Mr Hawkins' parked van was
OL,9,Fhanded to police. Officers are
OL,10,Finvestigating but no arrests have yet
OL,11,Fbeen made.
OL,13,F29 out of 45 police forces in the UK
OL,14,Fresponded to the FoI request. In
OL,15,FWales, Gwent Police recorded a 31%
OL,16,Fincrease and North Wales Police
OL,17,Frecorded a 6% decrease, while South
OL,18,FWales Police and Dyfed-Powys Police
OL,19,Fdid not respond.
