OL,7,FBut the insurance company who
OL,8,Fsubmitted the FoI request, Direct
OL,9,FLine, said the number of tool thefts
OL,10,Fis likely higher, as not all thefts
OL,11,Fare reported to police.
OL,13,FElectrician Lee Jones, 38, who works
OL,14,Facross Cardiff and Gwent, estimates he
OL,15,Flost #5,000 of tools when his van was
OL,16,Fbroken into earlier this year in
OL,17,FLlandaff.
