OL,7,FThe 38-year-old, from Cardiff, said:
OL,8,F"It happened in broad daylight.
OL,9,FThieves pulled up in a car behind my
OL,10,Fvan outside a property I was working
OL,11,Fin. It took them 30 seconds to cut a
OL,12,Fhole in the back door of my van, and
OL,13,Ftwo minutes to empty it."
OL,15,FMr Jones said he was unable to work
OL,16,Ffor a few weeks after the incident as
OL,17,Fhe had to replace the tools. No
OL,18,Farrests have been made.
