OL,7,FHe added: "It's not just a financial
OL,8,Fimpact. It's your career. It's
OL,9,Feverything."JSome tradespeople have
OL,10,Ftaken it upon themselves to tackle
OL,11,Ftool theft.
OL,13,FCarpenter Matthew Griffin, from
OL,14,FSwansea, has been encouraging
OL,15,Ftradespeople in Wales to register the
OL,16,Fserial numbers of their tools on his
OL,17,Fapp, Tool Archive, so second-hand
OL,18,Fbuyers can check if they are buying
OL,19,Fstolen tools.
