OL,7,FThe 27-year-old said: "My friends have
OL,8,Fhad to cancel holidays to replace
OL,9,Fstolen tools. I've seen careers ruined
OL,10,Fand people pushed to breaking point.
OL,12,F"My father is also a tradesman and
OL,13,FI've seen him distraught when he's had
OL,14,Fhis tools stolen. The gangs who are
OL,15,Fdoing this do not give a care in the
OL,16,Fworld."
