OL,7,FTrades United, a campaign group, said
OL,8,Fit wants to see more restrictions on
OL,9,Fselling second-hand power tools at
OL,10,Fbare minimum prices. The problem, they
OL,11,Fsaid, is that thieves can sell tools
OL,12,Fat unregulated car boot sales without
OL,13,Fworrying about getting caught.
OL,15,FShoaib Awan, a gas engineer from
OL,16,FLondon, set up the group after his
OL,17,FTransit Custom van was broken into
OL,18,Ftwice.
