OL,7,FThe second time, #8,500 worth of tools
OL,8,Fwas stolen from him, forcing him to
OL,9,Fcancel a holiday with his wife and two
OL,10,Fyoung daughters.
OL,12,FHe explained: "Tools worth thousands
OL,13,Fof pounds are being sold for less than
OL,14,F50 quid in cash at markets and car
OL,15,Fboot sales. What some tradespeople
OL,16,Fdon't realise is that they buy it from
OL,17,Fthere, then they get their vans broken
OL,18,Finto, and it ends up there again.
