OL,7,F"It is a plague. It's forcing
OL,8,Ftradespeople to leave the industry.
OL,9,FBritain is losing a lot of skilled
OL,10,Fworkers because of this."
OL,12,FA South Wales Police spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid: "We urge people not to buy what
OL,14,Fcould be stolen tools. Thieves will
OL,15,Flook to sell items on to make quick
OL,16,Fmoney, and this form of theft will
OL,17,Fcontinue for as long as there are
OL,18,Fwilling buyers.
