OL,7,FMark Summerville, from Direct Line, an
OL,8,Finsurance company supporting
OL,9,Ftradespeople, said: "It's important
OL,10,Fthat all instances of tool theft are
OL,11,Freported so police forces and
OL,12,Flawmakers understand the full extent
OL,13,Fof the issue helping them to identify
OL,14,Foffender patterns and to allocate
OL,15,Fresources to combat these crimes.
OL,17,F"Our data shows the value of each tool
OL,18,Ftheft claim is actually on the rise,
OL,19,Feven though the overall volume of
OL,20,Fclaims is moving downwards.
