OL,7,F"Further research from us found that
OL,8,F75 per cent of people would not feel
OL,9,Fconfident identifying stolen tools
OL,10,Fbeing resold. Tighter rules around
OL,11,Fproviding proof of purchase when
OL,12,Fselling second-hand tools could help
OL,13,Fmake it harder for criminals to resell
OL,14,Fgoods and could help reduce the
OL,15,Ffrequency of these thefts."
